@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### 1. 未登入被拒 - 應該回傳 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/signup

### 2. 註冊學員帳號
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student2@example.com",
  "password": "student123",
  "role": "student"
}

### 3. 登入管理員 - 取得 admin token
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "pass1234"
}

### 4. 登入學員 - 取得 student token
# @name studentLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student2@example.com",
  "password": "student123"
}

### 5. 學員報名
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{studentLogin.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "測試學員2",
  "email": "student2@test.com",
  "phone": "0987654321"
}

### 6. 管理員查看全部報名
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/signup
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}

### 7. 學員查看自己的報名
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/signup
Authorization: Bearer {{studentLogin.response.body.token}}

### 8. 學員嘗試刪除別人的資料 - 應該回傳 403 權限不足
# 先手動從步驟6的回應中取得其他人的 participant ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/signup/6959380941942232edfae127
Authorization: Bearer {{studentLogin.response.body.token}}

### 9. 管理員刪除資料 - 應該成功回傳 200
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/signup/6959380941942232edfae127
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}